    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for Model Risk Level 2. Six factors appropriately scoped out per MRL 2 guidance. Validation error of 12.4% mean relative error for NIH is within the 20% acceptance threshold. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support regulatory decision-making for the Class II CPB device hemolysis assessment. The acceptance criterion of RH not exceeding 1.65 has been verified across all five operating conditions, and the model is accepted for submission.",
